window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>She woke up on a spaceship with magical powers and incredible abilities. Now, she must save the universe from falling into darkness.</i></b></p> <p>Elle thought her summer would be ordinaryâ€”until she wakes up on a spaceship with newfound magic and incredible physical abilities. Suddenly, the fate of the universe rests in her hands.</p> <p>A mysterious Darkness is spreading, consuming planets, including Elle's home. With her new powers, Elle joins a daring team on an interstellar quest to find ancient relics that could stop the Darkness.</p> <p>Facing monstrous creatures, deciphering cryptic clues, and unleashing her incredible abilities, Elle and her friends must race against time. Can they save their worlds and loved ones from eternal shadow?</p> <p>Dive into the Dark Stars Trilogy and embark on a journey where high-tech sci-fi meets traditional fantasy magic. Perfect for fans of thrilling space adventures, characters who grow stronger with every challenge, and the power of teamwork.</p> <p><b>Download the Dark Stars Trilogy and be transported to a universe where second chances are real!</b></p>"; 
